Class MyShape

  • java.lang.Object
    • MyShape
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MyBoundedShape, MyLine

    public abstract class MyShape
extends Object
implements Serializable
    This abstract class implements Serializable so the it's variables can be serialized or deserialized, and implements the state and behaviour of all shapes.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
